Downloading
-----------
For Windows:
    Download and install Python 2.7 from http://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.7.3/python-2.7.3.msi
    Download and install GTK+ 2.24 from http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/binaries/win32/pygtk/2.24/pygtk-all-in-one-2.24.2.win32-py2.7.msi

Instalation
-----------

For Ubuntu:
    With the PIP:

        sudo pip install sanaviron-*.tar.gz

    Without PIP:

        Unpack archive - tar xvfz sanaviron-*.tar.gz

        Go to the folder sanaviron-* - cd sanaviron-*

        And run the installation script - sudo python setup.py install